{"tid":1465563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再互屌啦!","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:44.000Z","uid":175168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2db64be496ee34c9b16fc27247bb7b64283eaaf0","tid":1465563,"uid":175168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"依家政府就係想你地分化...<br />\n從內部自爆....<br />\n<br />\n大家再互屌就正中林鄭下懷!!<br />\n<br />\n不如大家諗下跟住落黎應該點做仲好!!!"},{"pid":"43c5fae3b84f86f8dbb035408779b7a42c3f7246","tid":1465563,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e44e687f57ec1d82ed9eb6c20d3f82807e1806a","tid":1465563,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhi"},{"pid":"c1b837775c79aa5893ec086288758c5ce36500e3","tid":1465563,"uid":175168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6fcc12047e6162b7bdffc0b39d7247d3a6ac6bdd","tid":1465563,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"054626d7307ccf2b86c97058eec82a3432b2eb61","tid":1465563,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"6216aee58e202e8862c57980ba46af51d90bb47e","tid":1465563,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"bf6de8c0c1e50fed810e90f7894db7e2d4685c9e","tid":1465563,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"P牌無quota開post，借貼<br />\n<br />\n813係好混亂既一日....<br />\n<br />\n1. 有手足block check-in 想快速地癱瘓機場 /令航班取消，<span style=\"color: red;\">但同時好多手足反對，因為令到旅客充滿怨氣 / 變相輸民意。</span><br />\n2. 經過最近黑警做鬼既情況愈黎愈過份同愈目中無人，有手足係機場捉到鬼後，花大量時間圍鬼，<span style=\"color: red;\">但同時好多手足反對，因為覺得錯左焦點，而且因爲鬼係捉不完。</span><br />\n3. 有勇武派手足開始對機場內警犬進行比較激烈的反擊行為，反之然警方今次明顯表現比平常克制 （比較下顯得，並非真係克制），<span style=\"color: red;\">但同時有好多手足反對，因為係機場入面，係所有焦點，包括外國媒體下，係中了警方陷阱，係輸了形象和民意。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以所以，<br />\n係大家記得要團結，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割𥱊，不篤灰</span></span>的大前提下，813的混亂，大家屌過嬲過迷茫過後，<br />\n希望可以理性咁大家好好討論反個共識，<br />\n可以重新開始，進行止蝕工程。<br />\n要記得！<br />\n我地由69開始，去到今日不容易，<br />\n我地既付出，係唔會因爲一日既挫折就走向下波。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煲底下的約定</span>，不要忘了。<br />\n屌完，豬隊友還是你最愛的香港手足。<br />\n邊撚個未豬過未7過？？<br />\n<br />\n所以麻煩大家重點諗諗：<br />\n1. 以後面對鬼的態度和做法。<br />\n2. 在機場內面對警犬的boundary。<br />\n3. 如何最有效影響機管局正常運作。<br />\n4. 如果重新重拾民意，表達對旅客歉意。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油。<br />\n我愛你們。</span></span>"},{"pid":"6bf2c42c1a5879dfe74de963298d535baf61e2fd","tid":1465563,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:47.000Z","msg":"黑警帶風向引互屌，冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94324daa0f0977fb1eaa688dbdacbed22fe8126d","tid":1465563,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"67d883a1830c529b603daeb9646cabce03672e62","tid":1465563,"uid":175168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:44.000Z","msg":"推!!"}]}